ActIndian Act
SubjectFort William First Nation - Grand Trunk Pacific Railway Settlement ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder a) authorizing the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to execute, on behalf of Her Majesty in Right of Canada, the Fort William First Nation Grand Trunk Pacific Railway SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT between Canada and the FORT WILLIAM FIRST NATION; and (2) accepting the absolute surrender to Canada of all rights and interests, pursuant to sections 38 and 39 of the Indian Act, of the lands.
